---
// Language Switcher Component - Desktop/Tablet Version
---

<div class="hidden sm:flex items-center space-x-2 text-sm uppercase tracking-widest">
    <button class="language-btn px-2 py-1 rounded transition-colors duration-200 hover:bg-med-sage hover:text-white" data-lang="es">ES</button>
    <button class="language-btn px-2 py-1 rounded transition-colors duration-200 hover:bg-med-sage hover:text-white" data-lang="en">EN</button>
    <button class="language-btn px-2 py-1 rounded transition-colors duration-200 hover:bg-med-sage hover:text-white" data-lang="fr">FR</button>
    <button class="language-btn px-2 py-1 rounded transition-colors duration-200 hover:bg-med-sage hover:text-white" data-lang="it">IT</button>
    <button class="language-btn px-2 py-1 rounded transition-colors duration-200 hover:bg-med-sage hover:text-white" data-lang="zh">中文</button>
</div>

<style>
    .language-btn.active {
        @apply bg-med-sage text-white font-medium;
    }

    .language-btn:not(.active) {
        @apply text-med-clay hover:text-white;
    }
</style>